// Tornado — the adversarial-bisection stressor (rfc_001 §9 + §3).
// CLEAN-ROOM (traffic.cpp:295-308): per-digit rotate-by-((xr*k+1)/2 - 1).
//   for n=2, k=8, xr=1: rotation = ((8+1)/2 - 1) = 3 → each row sends to the
//   node 3 hops "around the diagonal" — maximum bisection pressure.
